id=dkma_monster
name=DKMA Monster (Keep My Apps Alive)
version=v1.0.0
versionCode=10000
author=DKMA Monster
description=Universal Don't-Kill-My-App enforcer. On every boot it re-applies Doze whitelist, standby buckets, and background/autostart appops for the apps you list in /data/adb/dkma/apps.list — so aggressive OEM battery managers can't kill them.
